ZH: 在考古学家的发现中，陪葬的物品往往能帮助人们了解古人的生活方式。
EN: In archaeological discoveries, grave goods often help people understand the way of life of ancient people.

ZH: 我们在古墓中发现了许多陪葬品，这些物品非常珍贵。
EN: We found many grave goods in the ancient tomb, which are very precious.

ZH: 这座古墓的陪葬品展示出古代贵族的奢华生活。
EN: The grave goods of this ancient tomb display the luxurious life of the nobility.

ZH: 考古团队正在仔细清理李小姐的陪葬品。
EN: The archaeological team is carefully cleaning Miss Li's grave goods.

ZH: 这些陪葬的物品都是经过严格筛选的。
EN: These grave goods have all been carefully selected.

ZH: 陶俑是古代陪葬品的常见形式之一。
EN: Pottery figurines are a common form of grave goods in ancient times.

ZH: 这次发现的陪葬品将会被送往博物馆进行展示。
EN: The grave goods discovered this time will be sent to the museum for display.

ZH: 他们在古墓中找到了陪葬的青铜器。
EN: They found bronze ware buried with the deceased in the ancient tomb.

ZH: 这些花瓶是古代陪葬的文物之一。
EN: These vases are one of the artifacts buried with the deceased in ancient times.

ZH: 古代君主的陪葬品通常都十分豪华。
EN: The grave goods of ancient monarchs are usually very luxurious.

ZH: 这些陪葬品的价值远远超出了金钱。
EN: The value of these grave goods far exceeds money.

ZH: 王尼玛为她爱狗准备了最豪华的陪葬品。
EN: Wang Nima prepared the most luxurious grave goods for her beloved dog.

ZH: 这座古墓的陪葬品尽数损毁，考古学家们正在尽力修复。
EN: The grave goods of this ancient tomb are mostly damaged, and archaeologists are working hard to repair them.

ZH: 考古学家在挖掘的过程中逐渐发现了陪葬品的分布规律。
EN: Archaeologists gradually discovered the distribution pattern of grave goods during the excavation process.

ZH: 这些陪葬的物品将帮助我们了解过去社会的财富分配情况。
EN: These grave goods will help us understand the distribution of wealth in past societies.

ZH: 在古墓中发现的陪葬品规模宏大，显示出当时的社会地位。
EN: The massive grave goods found in the ancient tomb indicate the social status at that time.

ZH: 这些陪葬物品将被送到博物馆进行展览，让更多人了解古代风俗。
EN: These grave goods will be sent to the museum for exhibition, so that more people can understand ancient customs.

ZH: 考古学家通过分析陪葬品的特征确认了这座古墓的年代。
EN: Archaeologists confirmed the age of this ancient tomb by analyzing the characteristics of the grave goods.

ZH: 这些珍贵的陪葬品将成为人们学习古代文化的重要资料。
EN: These precious grave goods will become important materials for people to study ancient cultures.
